<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858336573097825.png" title="1718858336573097825.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-20 123737.png" width="836" height="509" style="width: 836px; height: 509px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">为了深入学习贯彻党的二十大精神，以及习近平总书记关于青年学生服务乡村振兴战略的重要指示，经济管理学院特别推出2024年暑期“三下乡”社会实践活动。本次活动旨在选拔出一批政治立场坚定、学习成绩优良、组织能力强、具有奉献精神的同学，为暑期“三下乡”注入活力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858382980092818.png" title="1718858382980092818.png" style="text-align: center; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858382229089759.png" title="1718858382229089759.png" style="text-align: center; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858381079087051.png" style="" title="1718858381079087051.png"/><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858382933058707.png" title="1718858382933058707.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858382980092818.png" style="" title="1718858382980092818.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（往期回顾）</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 31.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1.招募详情</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（一）招募对象</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经济管理学院在校学生</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（二）报名时间</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">6月18日—6月20日12：00</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（三）报名方式</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">招募微信群</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858542702018305.png" title="1718858542702018305.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-20 124213.png" width="817" height="833" style="width: 817px; height: 833px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">2.选拔要求</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">1、参与活动须家长知情且同意，思想端正、作风正派， 遵守国家法律规定，遵守校规校纪，无违纪情况，积极进步；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">2、热爱集体，团结同学，尊师敬长，有较强的集体荣 誉感和团队精神；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">3、热爱公益事业、具有服务精神，有从事志愿工作或 有相关志愿服务经验；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;">4、拥有较好的组织与协调能力，随机应变活动中突发 的各种紧急情况。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify;">5、意志坚定，服从组织安排与管理，积极主动配合团 队开展活动，除不可抗力因素外不可中途退出。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify;">6、有较强的工作能力和组织能力，有较强的工作责任 心和奉献精神，具有开拓创新意识，思维积极活跃，能够创 造性开展工作，其中有以下能力优先：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">①文艺表演能力；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">②材料撰写、摄影剪辑能力；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">③电商直播能力；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">④理论知识能力；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">⑤团干部优先；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">⑥有志愿服务、三下乡、返家乡社会实践经验者优先。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3.选拔流程</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1、报名：在规定时间内填写报名表，进群。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2、面试：携带报名表（一式三份）参加面试，面试内容主要为自我介绍、知识问答、分享志愿服务经历等。面试时间预计为6月20日晚7点，地点待定。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3、终审：根据面试情况，进行最终审核，并将最终人选通知入选同学。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240620/1718858721630067622.png" title="1718858721630067622.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-20 124226.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">三下乡，我们肩并肩，手挽手，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">共同筑梦，共同前行。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让知识的光芒，照亮每一个角落，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让希望的种子，在这片土地上生根发芽。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">来吧，朋友们，加入我们的行列，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">一起为乡村振兴，贡献青春的力量。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让我们的梦想，在这片土地上绽放，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让三下乡的旗帜，飘扬在希望的田野上。</span></p>